data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bed, 2 bath home on a 1.2-acre corner lot. Enjoy the convenience of a one-story layout and the luxury of a 3-car garage. The open floor plan and abundance of natural light create a bright and inviting atmosphere. This home has never flooded, providing peace of mind. Covered back porch perfect for entertaining. Plenty of room to expand. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
